{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_07_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 別々の輝きだからこそ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "M！　V！　撮！　影！　ですよー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is M! V! Shooting!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.2951474984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、テンションがまた高くないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ your energy seems high again‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2951474984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうですよ！\nなんてったって、今日は憧れのあの曲……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nAfter all‚ today we're shooting the new MV",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.248435545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "『GIRI-GIRI borderless\nworld』の新MVの撮影なんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for that admired song…\n\"GIRI-GIRI borderless world\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.422607692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装も、気に入ってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like you really like the new outfits too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.422607692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　すっごく気に入ってます！\n結果的に、衣装は新しいデザインで作りましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I really love them!\nEven though the outfits were designed with a new style…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.179002571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと以前のリズノワらしさも踏まえて\nデザインしてもらったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they still kept the essence of LizNoir\nfrom before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.802494939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今回はこころと一緒に\nどこかにかっこいいアドリブを入れよう、って話してて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ I was talking with Kokoro about\nadding some cool ad-libs this time around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。こころとも、仲直り出来たのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Did you manage to patch things up with Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4676679611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2790059566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、その節はご迷惑をおかけしました……！\nおかげで、ちゃんとこころと向き合えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ sorry for causing trouble back then…\nBut thanks to that‚ I was able to face Kokoro properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9164996315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "こころも、本当は昔の衣装を着てみたい気持ちが\nあったそうです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro also mentioned she had feelings about wanting to\ntry on the old outfits…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8317955043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.6319291592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "でもそれは、自分自身の気持ち、願望でしかない\nだから過去の衣装じゃなく、新しくすべきだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But those were just her own feelings and desires.\nSo‚ she said we should go with something new rather than the past outfits‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6666685741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "グサグサきました……\n確かに、こころの言ってること、もっともだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and it really struck a chord with me…\nIndeed‚ I understood where Kokoro was coming from.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.0666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2446527957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "その上「愛が追いかけてるのは二人のリズノワだけど\n今のファンが観たいのは四人のリズノワだ」と言われ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of that‚ when I was told‚\n\"Even though Ai is chasing after the LizNoir of two people‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8666711171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7025869209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "こころが本当にファンの人達を大事にしてることが……\nすっごく考えてることが良く分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the fans now want to see the LizNoir of four‚\"\nI really understood how much Kokoro values the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6000019073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……愛は、こころの気持ちを\nちゃんと聞いて納得出来たんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Ai‚ you really listened and\ncame to an understanding with Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8999993641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3253281432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　譲れないところは譲れませんでしたよ！\n……こころも、分かってくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! There were parts I couldn't compromise on…\n…And Kokoro understood that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5333326975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.1299765108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "この曲をずっと好きでいる人がいて、リメイクしても\n曲のイメージは大切にしなければならないこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She made it clear that there are people who have loved this song for a long time‚\nand even if we remake it‚ we must preserve the essence of the song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4522502738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "この曲に励まされた思い出を\n私やこころだけが持っている訳じゃないこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just me and Kokoro who hold these memories of\nbeing encouraged by this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9666634876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.6309806663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "だから、全く新しいものじゃなくて\nちゃんと今までのリズノワらしさも残したいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I wanted to keep not just something completely new‚\nbut also the LizNoir essence we've had up until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0771945844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今回のデザインは二人のリズノワらしさも\nしっかり残したものになっているんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why the design this time also firmly preserves\nthe LizNoir essence of both of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0878080781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.9866263864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "ぶつかって、理解し合って、より良いものへ……\n私達、ちゃんと出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We clashed‚ understood each other‚ and created something better…\nWe managed to do it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1000054676,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7399.992752200006,
          "startTime": 141.4999982198
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4477148213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　こころとかっこいいアドリブの\n確認をしてきますね！　では！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! I'm going to go confirm the cool ad-libs\nwith Kokoro! See you later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5000054676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、行ってらっしゃい……って、またいない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ take care… and she's gone again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4613426683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.6043415536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影本番",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――MV Shooting on air",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1863569417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
